Depay said: 'I am pleased that we have achieved a breakthrough and I have extended with the club.

'I want to develop myself in this team, which last season embarked on a plan for success.

I want to play for trophies and make myself important for the team.'

Depay has made an impressive start to the Dutch season, scoring five goals in three appearances.

